      "text": "拝啓、秋涼の折、ますますご繁栄のことと\nお慶び申し上げます――",
      "startTime": 227.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、次の仕事の件ですけど\n……誰に手紙を書いてるんですか？",
      "startTime": 234.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "里帰りライブの後、怜のお父さんから丁寧なお返事を\nいただいたんだ。俺も返事を返さないと失礼だろう？",
      "startTime": 240.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "二人して、律儀というかなんというか……\nそんなの、言ってくれれば私が伝えておくのに",
      "startTime": 248.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ読んでみるか？\n怜のことも心配してるみたいだぞ",
      "startTime": 254.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "よ、読みません！　お父さんってば\nなんでそんな恥ずかしいこと書いてるのよ！",
      "startTime": 260.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいことは書いてないって。じゃ、俺が読むよ\n「娘は頑固なところがありますが、根は優しい子で」",
      "startTime": 267.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "音読しないで下さい！　あと頑固じゃありません！\nお父さんの方が何倍も頑固なくせに、なんなのよもぉ",
      "startTime": 277.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "私へのメッセは短いのに、手紙はやけに長文だし……\n{user}さん、その手紙返して下さい！",
      "startTime": 288.7666809082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺宛にきたんだけど……\nとりあえず、返事を書いちゃうから",
      "startTime": 295.8666809082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_03-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "それも、後で何を書いたか教えてもらいますからね！\nはぁ……お父さんって、ほんと分かんないわね",
      "startTime": 304.2000142415,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}